# 🐍 Snake Game

A classic Snake Game built using Python and the Turtle graphics library.

## Features

- Snake movement
- Food generation
- Score system
- High score tracking
- Collision detection
- Snake growth

## Technologies

- Python
- Turtle
- Random
- Time

